# An Overview of using Acrolinx

Acrolinx is an editing software which helps you to ensure that your content is free of grammar, punctuation, brand related, and style issues. Although you can use Acrolinx both in the GitHub and Visual Studio Code tools, using it in Visual Studio Code is more interactive.

